<p>
	These three luxury shea butter bath melts from Heyland &amp; Whittle come in a handy bag making them a lovely gift or gesture for someone special. The bag contains one cornflower, one marigold and one rose bath melt. They are made in England using the finest natural ingredients and are sulphate and paraben free. To use simply drop the bath melt of your choice into a bath of warm water and allow it to melt, releasing the beautiful aroma of the essential oils. You can use it all or take it out after a while and use again for another bath.</p>
